# THIS CODE WILL LIGHT UP THE PIN
# MEANT TO BE USED WHEN THE PI DETECTS A COIN AND IS ABOUT TO TAKE A PICTURE
# FOR USER CONVENIENCE WHEN THE USER THEMSELVES IS CONTROLLING THE CONVEYOR BELT

import RPi.GPIO as GPIO
import time

led = 17

GPIO.setmode(GPIO.BCM)
GPIO.setwarnings(False)
GPIO.setup(led,GPIO.OUT)

print ("LED on")
GPIO.output(led,GPIO.HIGH)

time.sleep(3)

print("LED off")
GPIO.output(led,GPIO.LOW)




